{"type": "article", "id": 36673, "title": "用这些装了小房子的云，让小朋友建一座空中村庄｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-01-10T23:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 21020, "name": "Feist Forest"}, {"id": 25628, "name": "Mininch"}, {"id": 36634, "name": "Miscellaneous Adventures"}, {"id": 36635, "name": "AGAVE"}, {"id": 36636, "name": "IDEASKETCH"}, {"id": 36637, "name": "James Paulius"}, {"id": 36638, "name": "Federico Churba"}, {"id": 36639, "name": "Axel Peemöller"}, {"id": 36640, "name": "Dimitris Papazoglou"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 169, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170110215515NJEalQPdfij7o2Sv.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Sky Villages by James Paulius</h3><p>还记得那个能指路还能玩的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/36317.html\">指示板</a>吗？在为小朋友设计的建筑中，积木似乎是一个不会缺席的要素，美国设计师 <a href=\"http://jamespaulius.com/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\">James Paulius</a> 最近为布鲁克林儿童博物馆（Brooklyn Children’s Museum）旗下的 <a href=\"http://www.brooklynkids.org/spark/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SPARK</a> 游乐园打造了一个互动艺术装置。Paulius 为它取名为 Sky Villages，在以天空为背景的墙上设置了用来装积木的木质云朵以及大大小小的房屋基座。小朋友们可以尽情地从云里掏出小房子，根据自己的想象力把它们建成一座座空中村庄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215646OoG6w4p3dgW7LMhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701102156462SATUHWZl6J35CB7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017011021565189bjEm56Pv3wge4V.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334328\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215646VGJdZhenFBfqtO06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215646XmBCEwMi8OPnIj6H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215645ntCL3yFMDbPfYkr6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>DOUKET by mininch</h3><p>在忽冷忽热的天气里或者经常在室内室外两种环境间出入，不管是拿着外套到处走还是为此携带一个大包出门都很麻烦。为了一口气解决收纳问题，台湾设计品牌 <a href=\"http://mininch.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mininch</a> 推出了这款将能当包用的外套 DUOKET。外套本身都是简单利落的素色，内含多个容量不一的口袋，有些还采用了隐蔽式的拉链，在不牺牲外观的情况下提升安全性。经过精心设计的外套结构可以保证在拉上拉链的情况下，所有放在口袋中的物品在变化的过程中都能保持在原来的位置。以后再进入温暖的室内，只要脱下后简单折叠就能转换成手提包了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2054052511/duoket-1-buy-2-go-jacket-and-bag-transformed-in-se\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701102159076SURDrqIzYfBvL4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.020710\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215907AKyBmkHLCv6JDwVT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708824\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215908531lnz0mHL8S7RU6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.688791\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>mashikaku by IDEASKETCH</h3><p>如果你喜欢四四方方的工整感，不妨来看看这个由东京设计公司 <a href=\"https://www.ideasketch.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">IDEASKETCH</a> 制作的“真四角”（mashikaku）字体。它实际上是设计师对日本“江户文字”中角字的不同诠释，这种江户时代所使用的广告字体笔划极粗，类似常见于图章的篆体。除了字体使用权本身，IDEASKETCH 还经营相关的定制业务，涵盖服饰、手机壳以及抱枕。如果你感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.mashikaku.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买到印有真四角的定制产品，你还能通过<a href=\"http://make.mashikaku.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>制作正方形的图标。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017011021581121tqUmBAaks6RnOQ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215805MNCRKSofxQpa19T8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215805ERxgefiH6zPOwT4J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215805JkXu4qf8TmDgR3N1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215805lzKbr7eE6c2INiy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.786154\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cherry Wren Snack Cup by Feist Forest</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.feistforest.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Feist Forest</a> 是一个来自英国的家居设计品牌，专门经营手工制作的办公木桌。除此之外，还会和设计师联手制作日常小物，这个名叫 Cherry Wren 的木质容器就是它和户外品牌 <a href=\"https://www.miscellaneousadventures.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Miscellaneous Adventures</a> 共同推出的合作款。名字中的 Wren 指的是一种名为鹪鹩的小鸟，设计师以它们短小的身材为灵感制作了圆鼓鼓的小碗，还配有带花纹的勺子，放在一端就成了“尾巴”，而小小的把手则是鸟嘴。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.feistforest.com/store/cherry-wren-snack-cup\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 65 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701102157512PeXLf4y5FwhQKaA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215751gE9dpS3RGtcwT7Hj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701102157512IzQmpAujSVwYKFH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pillows by fCH</h3><p>这套看起来像是水彩打翻在布料上的枕头是阿根廷设计师 <a href=\"http://www.federicochurba.com.ar/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Federico Churba</a> 和布宜诺斯艾利斯的纺织品牌 <a href=\"http://www.agavetextiles.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">AGAVE</a> 推出的合作款。Churba 选择的都是比较淡雅的大地色系，可以很好地融入浅色系装饰风格或是木质家具间。枕头上的“水渍”有深有浅，显得自然随性，仿佛可以追溯出它是如何缓慢扩散开来的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215722o9gXFlpKCZ5U8izL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215723UmqHh7rl4LYiWB35.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215723lFkA0cL3mprsBV78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215723DzEWoe4PatwU12hX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Festival identity by Axel Peemoeller &amp; Dimitris Papazoglou</h3><p>从电影相关的元素中汲取灵感，美国设计师 <a href=\"http://axelpeemoeller.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Axel Peemöller</a> 与希腊设计师 <a href=\"http://www.dimitrispapazoglou.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dimitris Papazoglou</a> 合作为去年 11 月举行的第 57 届希腊塞萨洛尼基电影节（Thessaloniki International Film Festival）打造了一套黑白两色的平面设计。这种不断重复的排版方式让人很容易将它们与银幕、电影的每一帧以及影院中的一排排座位联系起来，看似杂乱无章却有一种统一的美感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201701102155577GENaOpD6TcyZm20.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017011021555970FvasZnEGoBqNkT.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215556zdGNu1iaeVB83hqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215557UGvHykJTZxfLbeoh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215557pJAhU0ydM68bziP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170110215556cKfn8mQLI9kYAM7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}